== 歷史 ==
{{main|老挝历史}}
=== 早期历史 ===
{{参见|真腊}}
[[Image:Plainofjars_2.jpg|thumb]]是东南亚最重要的史前遗址之一，2019年被列为[[世界遗产|世界遗产]]]]
最晚在10万年前，老挝境内已经有人类居住<ref name="baike"/>。老挝北部[[安南山脉|安南山脉]]的{{le|丹巴灵洞穴|Tam Pa Ling Cave}}出土了距今46,000年前的现代人类头骨化石，是截至目前东南亚年代最久远的人类化石考古发现<ref>{{Cite journal|pmid = 22908291|pmc = 3437904|year = 2012|author1 = Demeter|first1 = F|title = Anatomically modern human in Southeast Asia (Laos) by 46 ka|journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|volume = 109|issue = 36|pages = 14375–80|last2 = Shackelford|first2 = L. L.|last3 = Bacon|first3 = A. M.|last4 = Duringer|first4 = P|last5 = Westaway|first5 = K|last6 = Sayavongkhamdy|first6 = T|last7 = Braga|first7 = J|last8 = Sichanthongtip|first8 = P|last9 = Khamdalavong|first9 = P|last10 = Ponche|first10 = J. L.|last11 = Wang|first11 = H|last12 = Lundstrom|first12 = C|last13 = Patole-Edoumba|first13 = E|last14 = Karpoff|first14 = A. M.|doi = 10.1073/pnas.1208104109}}</ref>。在老挝北部还发现了属于[[和平文化|和平文化]]的石器，年代可追溯至[[更新世|更新世]]晚期<ref>{{Cite journal|year = 2009|author1 = White|first1 = J.C.|title = Archaeological investigations in northern Laos: New contributions to Southeast Asian prehistory|journal = Antiquity|volume = 83|issue = 319|last2 = Lewis|first2 = H.|last3 = Bouasisengpaseuth|first3 = B.|last4 = Marwick|first4 = B.|last5 = Arrell|first5 = K|url = http://antiquity.ac.uk/projgall/white/|author = |access-date = 2019-07-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171010191403/http://antiquity.ac.uk/projgall/white/|archive-date = 2017-10-10|dead-url = no}}</ref>。考古证据表明，老挝境内的农业社会产生于公元前第4千年<ref>{{cite book|last1=Marwick|first1=Ben|last2=Bouasisengpaseuth|first2=Bounheung|chapter=History and Practice of Archaeology in Laos|editor1-last=Habu|editor1-first=Junko|editor2-last=Lape|editor2-first=Peter|editor3-last=Olsen|editor3-first=John|title=Handbook of East and Southeast Asian Archaeology|publisher=Springer|date=2017|chapter-url=https://osf.io/preprints/socarxiv/75zhc/|access-date=2020-09-17|archive-date=2019-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190706125232/https://osf.io/preprints/socarxiv/75zhc/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。根据墓葬考古结果，老挝大概在前1500年出现使用铜器的复杂社会，前700年出现铁器。在众多洞穴和墓葬考古遗址中，最著名者即位于[[川圹省|川圹]][[石缸平原|石缸平原]]的巨石文化，据信此遗址曾经孕育了贸易社会<ref name="Viravond">{{cite web |url = http://www.reninc.org/bookshelf/history_of_laos_viravong.pdf |title = HISTORY OF LAOS |author = Maha Sila Viravond |date =  |accessdate = 2017-12-29 |publisher = Refugee Educators' Network |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180509085854/http://www.reninc.org/bookshelf/history_of_laos_viravong.pdf |archive-date = 2018-05-09 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Manich">{{cite web |url = http://www.reninc.org/bookshelf/history_of_laos_manich.pdf |title = HISTORY OF LAOS (includlng the hlstory of Lonnathai, Chiangmai) |author = M.L. Manich |date =  |accessdate = 2017-12-29 |publisher = Refugee Educators' Network |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170517084823/http://www.reninc.org/bookshelf/history_of_laos_manich.pdf |archive-date = 2017-05-17 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

老挝最早的居民是[[澳洲人种|澳洲人种]]，后被[[孟-高棉语族|孟-高棉人]]取代<ref name="Cambridge University Press">{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/?id=0b-6wpalR40C&pg=PA102&lpg=PA102&dq=%5B%5BNeolithic+Revolution%7Cagricultural+expansion%5D%5D+Southeast+asia#v=onepage&q=%5B%5BNeolithic%20Revolution%7Cagricultural%20expansion%5D%5D%20Southeast%20asia&f=false |title=The Cambridge History of Southeast Asia, Volume One, Part One |publisher=Cambridge University Press |accessdate=2017-01-03|isbn=978-0-521-66369-4 |last1=Tarling |first1=Nicholas |year=1999 }}</ref>。孟-高棉人在老挝境内建立诸多古国，但关于此段历史的史料并不充足，因此关于史实有较多争议<ref name="WJB"/>。兴起于[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]的[[真腊|真腊]]和位于今越南南方海岸的[[占人|占人]]都曾在老挝南端的[[占巴塞省|占巴塞省]]建立定居地<ref name="Hal1985">{{cite book|author=Kenneth R. Hal|title=Maritime Trade and State Development in Early Southeast Asia|url=https://books.google.com/?id=ncqGAAAAIAAJ&q=funan+mountain+kings&dq=funan+mountain+kings|year=1985|publisher=University of Hawaii Press|isbn=978-0-8248-0843-3|page=63}}</ref><ref>National Library of Australia.  [http://www.nla.gov.au/asian/form/coedes2.html Asia's French Connection : George Coedes and the Coedes Collection] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nla.gov.au/asian/form/coedes2.html |date=20111021052224 }}</ref>。真腊在6世纪将今万象以南的土地占为己有<ref name="baike">{{cite book|author=中国大百科全书出版社汇编|year=1998 |title =[[中国大百科全书|中国大百科全书]]|edition=第一版|series=外国历史（一） |publisher=中国大百科全书出版社 |location=北京 |id= }}，第535页。</ref>，更是曾在占巴塞的湿梨多补罗（Shrestapura）定都，当地至今留有[[瓦普寺|瓦普寺]]，为[[世界遗产|世界遗产]]。8世纪，真腊分裂为水真腊和陆真腊，其中陆真腊即以老挝地区为中心。陆真腊以北，已经有[[泰语民族|泰语民族]]部落，隶属于[[南诏国|南诏国]]<ref name="baike"/>；亦有[[孟人|孟人]]建立的古国，如[[陀罗钵地|陀罗钵地]]、[[骇黎朋猜|骇黎朋猜]]等<ref name="Viravond"/><ref name="Manich"/>。

自8世纪至10世纪，泰老民族南迁，逐渐取代老挝的孟-高棉人<ref name="PittayawatPittayaporn">[http://www.manusya.journals.chula.ac.th/files/essay/Pittayawat%2047-68.pdf Pittayaporn, Pittayawat (2014). Layers of Chinese Loanwords in Proto-Southwestern Tai as Evidence for the Dating of the Spread of Southwestern Tai] {{Wayback|url=http://www.manusya.journals.chula.ac.th/files/essay/Pittayawat%2047-68.pdf |date=20150627063518 }}. ''MANUSYA: Journal of Humanities'', Special Issue No 20: 47–64.</ref>。
